"title": "8211: commitment, to the world",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8211: commitment, to the world",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Though the world is fallen, God still loves the world and is committed to it. Commitment by believers to worldly pursuits and evil is to be avoided as they are called upon to be “in the world” but “not of the world”.</p>\n<h2>Commitment to this world to be avoided because it is a fallen and sinful place</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">EPH 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16-1John2:17\">1JN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Though the world is fallen, God still loves it</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18-2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:18–5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Preoccupation with the things of this world is incompatible with holy living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15\">1JN 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14-John17:16\">JHN 17:14–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40\">ACT 2:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:31\">1CO 7:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14-2Cor6:17\">2CO 6:14–6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:11\">ISA 52:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:2\">COL 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14\">1PE 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:3\">1PE 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Commitment to the world is seen especially in materialism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:23\">MAT 19:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:24\">LUK 18:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h2>The outcome of worldly commitment</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual loss</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36\">MRK 8:36</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:32\">1CO 11:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:11\">JHN 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6\">EPH 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Carelessness with regard to Jesus Christ's return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:38-Matt24:39\">MAT 24:38–24:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:40\">LUK 12:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:46\">LUK 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:1-1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:1–5:9</a></p>",
